divs: Sighting DetailsAt about 11:45 AM, June 14, 2009 I stepped out of church and looked into the western sky and saw several "V" shaped contrails. These were obviously not a natural occurance and it was difficult to conceive that conventional jet aircraft could have turned this sharp. There were no aircraft in view when I observed these contrails. I took a picture with my cell phone (Nokia 6555). Sacramento International airport is about 10 miles away, in the direction I was facing.
